### Create a new course
POST http://localhost:3000/api/course
Content-Type: application/json

{

    "id": 1,
    "name": "HTTP Basics",
    "slug": "http-basics",
    "description": "A beginner-friendly course on HTTP.",
    "price": 9.99,
    "onSale": false,
    "displayPrice": null,
    "image": "http://example.com/image.jpg",
    "published": true,
    "completed": [1, 2, 3],
    "difficulty": "ALL_LEVELS",
    "paid": true,
    "instructorId": 1
}


### Get all courses
GET http://localhost:3000/api/courses


### Get one course
GET http://localhost:3000/api/course/http-basics










